fields.description:
Delete an existing binVote. 

THIS CANNOT BE UNDONE!
Example:
```
mutation{
  deleteBinVote (
    decisionId: 1
    id: 1
  ) {
    id
  }
}
```

returns
```
{
  "data": {
    "deleteBinVote": {
      "id": "1"
    }
  }
}
```
    or, when deleting a nonexistent record:
```
{
  "data": {
    "deleteBinVote": null
  }
}
```

